        By
        <span><a href="/person/p/janine-puhak">Janine Puhak</a><!----><span class="article-source"><a target="_blank" href="http://www.foxnews.com/"> | Fox News</a></span></span></span><!----></div><div class="article-social"><div class="social-icons"><ul><li class="fb"><a href="#" rel="nofollow">Facebook</a></li><li class="tw"><a href="#" rel="nofollow">Twitter</a></li><li class="flipboard"><a rel="nofollow">Flipboard</a></li><li class="comments"><a href="#" rel="nofollow"><span>Comments</span></a></li><li class="print"><a href="/food-drink/vegan-woman-in-italy-threatens-to-kill-mom-for-making-traditional-meat-sauce.print" rel="nofollow">Print</a></li><li class="email"><a href="#" rel="nofollow">Email</a></li></ul></div></div></div></header><div class="article-content-wrap sticky-columns"><div class="article-content"><div class="article-body"><div source="" class="image-ct featured featured-image"><div class="m"><picture><source media="(max-width: 767px)" srcset="https://a57.foxnews.com/static.foxnews.com/foxnews.com/content/uploads/2018/11/1470/828/meat-sauce-istock1.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1 2x"><source media="(min-width: 767px)" srcset="https://a57.foxnews.com/static.foxnews.com/foxnews.com/content/uploads/2018/11/1862/1048/meat-sauce-istock1.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1 2x"><img src="https://a57.foxnews.com/a57.foxnews.com/static.foxnews.com/foxnews.com/content/uploads/2018/11/640/320/1862/1048/meat-sauce-istock1.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1?ve=1&amp;tl=1" alt="The vegan daughter told court officials that for a long time she had not had &quot;sensory nor olfactory contact” with animal products before moving to live with her mother."></picture></div><div class="info"><div class="caption"><p>
          The vegan daughter told court officials that for a long time she had not had &quot;sensory nor olfactory contact” with animal products before moving to live with her mother.
          <span>(iStock)</span></p></div></div></div><p class="speakable">Though many people would happily dig into a lovingly home-cooked meal from their parents, one vegan woman in Italy has been fined $1,170 for threatening to stab her mother for making traditional meat sauce in her presence.</p><div class="ad-container tablet"><div data-ad-pos="tablet" data-ad-size="300x250" data-ad-lz="" class="ad gpt ad-h-250"></div><!----></div><div class="ad-container mobile"><div data-ad-pos="mobile" data-ad-size="300x250" data-ad-lz="" class="ad gpt ad-h-250"></div><!----></div><p class="speakable">Italian newspaper <a href="http://gazzettadimodena.gelocal.it/modena/cronaca/2018/10/31/news/non-fare-il-ragu-o-ti-accoltello-condannata-la-figlia-vegana-1.17409253">Gazzetta di Modena</a> reported this week that the 48-year-old woman has been ordered by local courts to pay a $520 court fine and $650 to her mother for physically threatening her with a kitchen knife, after the sexagenarian whipped up Bolognese sauce in their newly shared home.</p><div data-ad-pos="inread" data-ad-size="1x1" class="ad gpt ad-h-1"></div><div source="" class="image-ct inline"><div class="m"><picture><source media="(max-width: 767px)" srcset="https://a57.foxnews.com/static.foxnews.com/foxnews.com/content/uploads/2018/11/1470/828/iStock-886084642.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1 2x"><source media="(min-width: 767px)" srcset="https://a57.foxnews.com/static.foxnews.com/foxnews.com/content/uploads/2018/11/1862/1048/iStock-886084642.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1 2x"><img src="https://a57.foxnews.com/static.foxnews.com/foxnews.com/content/uploads/2018/11/640/320/iStock-886084642.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1" alt="Furious with the smell of meat sauce simmering on the stove one day in March 2016, the daughter reportedly grabbed a knife and made a grave threat."></picture></div><div class="caption"><p>
      Furious with the smell of meat sauce simmering on the stove one day in March 2016, the daughter reportedly grabbed a knife and made a grave threat.
      <span class="copyright">(iStock)</span></p></div></div><p>According to <a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2018/11/01/italian-vegan-ordered-pay-400-fine-threatening-stab-mother-ragu/" target="_blank">The Telegraph</a>, the &#x201C;newly unemployed&#x201D; daughter had recently moved back into her mother&#x2019;s small apartment, where she often cooked in the rezdore tradition of chefs in the Emilia Romagna dialect.</p><p><strong><a href="https://www.foxnews.com/food-drink/oscar-mayer-says-hot-dogs-are-sandwiches-twitter-isnt-so-sure" target="_blank">OSCAR MAYER SAYS HOT DOGS ARE SANDWICHES; TWITTER ISN&apos;T SO SURE</a></strong></p><div class="ad-container mobile"><div data-ad-pos="mobile" data-ad-size="300x251" data-ad-lz="" class="ad gpt ad-h-250"></div><!----></div><p>The vegan daughter told court officials that, prior to moving to live with her mother,&#xA0;she had&#xA0;long been avoiding&#xA0;&quot;sensory&quot; and &quot;olfactory contact&#x201D; with animal products.</p><p>Lawyers further told the Gazzetta di Modena that there had been &#x201C;an escalation of aggressive episodes,&#xA0;always over food,&#x201D; before things nearly took a turn for the fatal.</p><p>Furious with the smell of meat sauce simmering on the stove one day in March 2016, the daughter reportedly grabbed a knife and made a grave threat.</p><p><strong><a href="http://Vegan%20woman%20fined%20%24650%20for%20threatening%20to%20kill%20her%20Italian%20mother%20for%20making%20meat%20sauce%20Though%20many%20people%20would%20happily%20dig%20into%20a%20lovingly%20home-cooked%20meal%20from%20their%20parents,%20one%20vegan%20woman%20in%20Italy%20has%20been%20fined%20%24650%20for%20threatening%20to%20stab%20her%20mother%20for%20making%20traditional%20meat%20sauce%20in%20her%20presence.%20%20On%20Oct.%2031,%20Italian%20newspaper%20Gazzetta%20di%20Modena%20reported%20that%20an%2048-year-old%20woman%20has%20been%20ordered%20by%20local%20courts%20to%20pay%20her%20mother%20%24650%20for%20physically%20threatening%20her%20with%20a%20kitchen%20knife,%20after%20the%2069-year-old%20whipped%20up%20Bolognese%20sauce%20in%20their%20newly%20shared%20home.%20%20According%20to%20the%20Telegraph,%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnewly%20unemployed%E2%80%9D%20daughter%20had%20recently%20moved%20back%20into%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20small%20apartment,%20where%20the%20sexagenarian%20often%20cooked%20in%20the%20rezdore%20tradition%20of%20chefs%20in%20the%20Emilia%20Romagna%20dialect.%20%20OSCAR%20MAYER%20SAYS%20HOT%20DOGS%20ARE%20SANDWICHES;%20TWITTER%20ISN&apos;T%20SO%20SURE%20The%20vegan%20daughter%20told%20court%20officials%20that%20she%20had%20long%20has%20%E2%80%9Cno%20sensory%20nor%20olfactory%20contact%E2%80%9D%20with%20animal%20products%20before%20moving%20to%20live%20with%20her%20mother,%20who%20often%20made%20the%20rich,%20meaty%20sauce.%20Lawyers%20further%20confirmed%20to%20the%20Gazzetta%20di%20Modena%20that%20there%20had%20been%20%E2%80%9Can%20escalation%20of%20aggressive%20episodes%20%E2%80%93%20always%20over%20food%E2%80%9D%20before%20things%20nearly%20took%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20fatal.%20Furious%20with%20the%20smell%20of%20meat%20sauce%20simmering%20on%20the%20stove%20one%20day%20in%20March%202016,%20the%20daughter%20reportedly%20grabbed%20a%20knife%20and%20made%20a%20grave%20threat.%20FOLLOW%20US%20ON%20FACEBOOK%20FOR%20MORE%20FOX%20LIFESTYLE%20NEWS%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20won%E2%80%99t%20stop%20on%20your%20own%20then%20I%E2%80%99ll%20make%20you%20stop.%20Quit%20making%20rag%C3%B9,%20or%20I%E2%80%99ll%20stab%20you%20in%20the%20stomach,%E2%80%9D%20the%20angry%20daughter%20said,%20as%20per%20the%20Telegraph,%20inciting%20her%20mother%20to%20press%20charges.%20%20With%20the%20complaint%20making%20its%20way%20to%20Modena%20tribunal%20court%20well%20over%20two%20years%20later,%20Justice%20of%20Peace%20Nadia%20Trifil%C3%B2%20ultimately%20ruled%20in%20favor%20of%20the%20mother.%20She%20smacked%20the%20daughter%20with%20a%20%24520%20court%20fine%20and%20ordered%20her%20to%20pay%20%24650%20to%20her%20mother%20as%20compensation.%20%20The%20identities%20of%20the%20mother%20and%20daughter%20remain%20unknown%20at%20this%20time.%20%20Naturally,%20the%20Twitterverse%20had%20a%20whole%20lot%20to%20say%20about%20the%20wild%20tale.%20%20%E2%80%9CThe%20existence%20of%20Bolognese%20sauce%20is%20definitely%20in%20the%20top%203%20on%20my%20list%20of%20reasons%20for%20why%20I&apos;m%20not%20a%20vegan,%E2%80%9D%20one%20said.%20%20%E2%80%9CMust%20need%20a%20steak,%E2%80%9D%20another%20clapped.%20%E2%80%9CSomeone%20needs%20some%20bacon%20in%20their%20life,%E2%80%9D%20another%20meat%20lover%20agreed.%20%20%E2%80%9CHad%20I%20been%20the%20judge,%20I%20would%20have%20jailed%20the%20daughter%20for%20attempted%20murder,%E2%80%9D%20one%20mused%20on%20a%20more%20serious%20note." target="_blank">FOLLOW US ON FACEBOOK FOR MORE FOX LIFESTYLE NEWS</a></strong></p><p>&#x201C;If you won&#x2019;t stop on your own then I&#x2019;ll make you stop. Quit making rag&#xFA;, or I&#x2019;ll stab you in the stomach,&#x201D; the angry daughter said, as per The Telegraph, inciting her mother to press charges.</p><p>With the complaint making its way to Modena tribunal court well over two years later, Justice of Peace Nadia Trifilo&#xA0;ultimately ruled in favor of the 69-year-old mother. She smacked the daughter with a $520 court fine and ordered her to pay $650 to her mother as compensation.</p><p>The identities of the mother and daughter were not disclosed.</p><p>Naturally, the Twitterverse had a whole lot to say about the wild tale.</p><div class="embed-media twitter"><div class="tweet-embed"></div></div><p>&#x201C;The existence of Bolognese sauce is definitely in the top 3 on my list of reasons for why I&apos;m not a vegan,&#x201D; one said.</p><div class="embed-media twitter"><div class="tweet-embed"></div></div><p>&#x201C;Must need a steak,&#x201D; another clapped.</p><div class="embed-media twitter"><div class="tweet-embed"></div></div><p>&#x201C;Someone needs some bacon in their life,&#x201D; another meat lover agreed.</p><div class="embed-media twitter"><div class="tweet-embed"></div></div><p>&#x201C;Had I been the judge, I would have jailed the daughter for attempted murder,&#x201D; one mused on a more serious note.</p><!----></div><div class="article-meta"><div class="author-bio">Janine Puhak is an editor for Fox News Lifestyle. Follow her on Twitter at <a href="https://twitter.com/@janinepuhak" target="_blank">@JaninePuhak</a></div></div><footer class="article-footer"><!----><!----><div data-uid="ar-2" class="vendor-unit tablet-desktop"></div><div data-uid="ar-3" class="vendor-unit tablet-desktop"></div><div data-uid="ar-1" class="vendor-unit mobile"></div><div class="vendor-unit vendor-yieldmo"><div class="ad-container mobile-tablet yieldmo"><div id="cu_article_4" class="ad cu"></div></div></div><div class="vendor-unit vendor-yieldmo"><div id="cu_article_3" class="ad-container yieldmo"></div></div><div data-uid="ar-8" class="vendor-unit tablet-desktop"></div><div id="commenting" class="article-comments"></div></footer></div><aside class="sidebar sidebar-article sidebar-primary desktop"><div class="sticky-region"><div class="sidebar-columns"><div class="ad-container desktop"><div data-ad-pos="desktop" data-ad-size="300x250,300x600" data-ad-lz="" class="ad gpt "></div><span class="advert-txt"></span></div><div data-uid="ar-4" class="vendor-unit"></div><section class="collection collection-trending"><header class="heading"><h4 class="title">Trending in Lifestyle</h4></header><div class="content"><ul><li><article class="article"><div class="m"><a href="https://www.foxnews.com/lifestyle/puppy-yoga-gaining-popularity-as-a-new-twist-on-the-workout"><picture><img src="https://a57.foxnews.com/static.foxnews.com/foxnews.com/content/uploads/2019/02/270/152/dog-yoga.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1" alt="Puppy yoga gaining popularity as a new twist on the workout"></picture></a></div><div class="info"><h5 class="title"><a href="https://www.foxnews.com/l